  txTime   validTime ->                                                   
                                                                          
         |  .  .  .  .  .  .  .  .  .                                     
         |  .  .  .  #  .  .  .  .  .   as-of tx=3 valid=3                
         |  .  .  #  #  .  .  .  .  .                                     
         |  .  #  #  O  .  .  .  .  .   { worker:42 status = "active" }   
         |  .  .  .  .  .  .  .  .  .                                     
         |  .  .  .  .  .  .  .  .  .                                     
         |  .  .  .  .  .  .  .  .  .   retract != tombstone != correct>  
                                                                          
                                                                          
                                                                          
                                                                          
  Read what we knew then about what was true then.                        
                                                                          
                                                                          ",
  "DERIVATION ALSO CONVERGES ("META")                                                
                                                                                  
                                                                                  
                                                                                  
  events   ----+----> derived facts      requires.kyc on worker:42                
                                                                                  
               +----> obligation       > [ ] "KYC form" -> [x]                    
                                                                                  
               +----> workflow run       step 2 unblocks                          
                                                                                  
               +----> generated view     row updates from same fold               
                                                                                  
                                                                                  
                                                                                  
  one fold per layer | no layer is separately synchronized                        
                                                                                  
